text: Mariella Venter (born 10 January 2000) is a South African competitive swimmer who specializes in the backstroke. She competed in the women's 100 metre backstroke at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:South African female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Female backstroke swimmers Category:Swimmers at the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for South Africa Category:Swimmers at the 2018 Commonwealth Games
